             sworn. - I am a gunstock-maker, in <placeName id="t18040912-58-crimeloc347">Albion-street, Commercial-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18040912-58-crimeloc347" type="placeName" value="Albion-street, Commercial-road"></interp>
