                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040912-58-off344 t18040912-58-crimeloc347"></join>; I knew these pipes to be mine; that is, they were on my premises.</p>
               <p>Q. Who is your landlord? - 
               <persName id="t18040912-58-person657">A. Joshua Buley</persName>
            ; they were fixed on since I was tenant to him, they come through the house into the back yard, I have got the other piece that I was forced to cut off.</p>
               <p>Q. Do they match? - A. Yes.</p>
